# RI-Proyecto-G3 - Global .gitignore for ESP-IDF (C) monorepo

# Build outputs and generated component artifacts
**/build/
**/managed_components/

# IDE workspace settings (local only)
**/.vscode/

# ESP-IDF dependency lock generated per app
**/dependencies.lock

# ESP-IDF runtime configuration (keep only defaults template)
**/sdkconfig
**/sdkconfig.*
!**/sdkconfig.defaults

# Compiled binaries and linker outputs
**/*.elf
**/*.bin
**/*.map
